# Optional: the read RPC the dApp uses for verification (read-only, no wallet).
# If unset, the app falls back to the `rpc` field baked into contract.json,
# then to a local chain. Set this to your own Sepolia RPC (Alchemy/Infura) for
# reliable reads. In Vercel, add it as the env var VITE_RPC_URL instead.
VITE_RPC_URL=
